00:00:54.820 --> 00:00:57.380
So please join me in welcoming
Brant and Patrick.

00:00:57.380 --> 00:01:00.880
[APPLAUSE]

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:03.142
BRANT COOPER: Thanks
for having us here.

00:01:03.142 --> 00:01:04.370
It's great to be here.

